  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n87/mode/1up">84</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n87/mode/1up">84</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. kaṇṇeṉap peyar koṭuttōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol ēḻāvatām. atu viṉaiceyyāniṟṟalākiya iṭattiṉkaṇṇum, nilamākiya iṭattiṉkaṇṇum, kālamākiya iṭattiṉkaṇṇumeṉa ammūvakaikkuṟippiṉkaṇṇuntōṉṟum. e-ṟu. eṉavē, ēḻāvatu iṭapporuṇmaitteṉṟavāṟām.</p>
<p>kuṟippiṟṟōṉṟumatuveṉṟatu avaṟṟaiyiṭamākak kuṟittavaḻi avvēṟṟumai tōṉṟumeṉṟavāṟu. eṉavē, iṭamākak kuṟikkappaṭātavaḻi appeyarkkaṇ vēṟṟumai tōṉṟāteṉpatām.</p>
<p>taṉṉiṉamuṭittaleṉpataṉāṉ ēṉaivēṟṟumaiccoṟkaḷum avvapporuṭkaṭkuṟippilvaḻi avvappeyarkkaṇ vārāmai koḷka.</p>
<p>u - m.</p> 
  <lg xml:id="TolC081-Cena-cit1">
  <l>taṭṭuppuṭaikkaṇ vantāṉ;</l>
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC081-Cena-cit2">
  <l>māṭattiṉ kaṇiruntāṉ;</l>
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC081-Cena-cit3">
  <l>kūtirkkaṇ vantāṉ</l>
  </lg>
  <p>eṉa varum.	(20)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
